casebody.data:
Steven T. HUMPHREY, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
STATE of Florida, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-1174 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. May 18, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

This appeal is dismissed on account of appellant's failure to comply with this court's order dated April 4, 2018, requiring appellant to submit a copy of the circuit court order or orders being appealed.

BLACK, SALARIO, and ROTHSTEIN-YOUAKIM, JJ, Concur.
